    <description>
        <p>
            A practical tool (for students, engineers and teachers) to provides calculation in practical works in fluid mechanic laboratory.
        </p>
        <p>
            Features:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Rolling ball viscometer;</li>
            <li>Pressure Measurement and Calibration;</li>
            <li>Calculation of the hydrostatic force and the location of the center of pressure;</li>
            <li>Calculations in orifice meter and Venturi;</li>
            <li>.....</li>
            <li>English GUI.</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
